                        <p>And then he fired.</p>
<p><i>[Okay, you know what, this article is already 9 hours late so I’m just gonna go ahead and publish it. Do better Bron, Jesus.]</i></p>
<p><i>Bron Maher is a Trinity junior. His column runs every other Wednesday. </i><i><br></i></p>

